{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/gamedev/game-jams","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I like jams. But I never win them.</p>\n<p>I have participated in several game jams:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://repl.it/talk/challenge/Were-hosting-a-Game-Jam/11432\">Repl.it Game Jam</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itch.io/jam/2020-epic-megajam\">Mega Jam 2020</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itch.io/jam/aiandgames-2021\">AI and Games 2021</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Only one of them was submitted <a href=\"https://replit.com/@stakanmartini/test-roguelike-11\">https://replit.com/@stakanmartini/test-roguelike-11</a>. Read longer story <a href=\"/gamedev/pyroguelike\">on its page</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"June 06, 2021","path":"/gamedev/game-jams","title":"Game Jams","section":null,"draft":null,"subtitle":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"pagePath":"/gamedev/game-jams","breadcrumb":{"location":"/gamedev/game-jams","crumbs":[{"pathname":"/","crumbLabel":"Index"},{"pathname":"/gamedev","crumbLabel":"gamedev"},{"pathname":"/gamedev/game-jams","crumbLabel":"game-jams"}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1291123867","2911207801","3388252522","447685113"]}